{"tid":2286603,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】石原里美加入寫真月曆戰　做咗人妻照曬性感小背心","createTime":"2020-11-15T06:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T08:13:05.000Z","uid":16659,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"20a41eea7c5998b1459c736771e8119dcf14a2ae","tid":2286603,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:39:22.000Z","msg":"每年年尾都是日本月曆銷售戰，繼早前61歲宮崎美子、38歲深田恭子加入戰團後，「日劇女王」石原里美日前亦宣布推出2021年寫真月曆。雖然上月宣布已閃嫁圈外才俊，但石原里美卻仍然非常大方，不但在月曆封面擺出撩人表情，更以湖水藍色小背心大騷Fit爆身材，非常有吸引力，相信能夠與其他對手一爭長短。"},{"pid":"eba5087d23b34f81c8c02c12c03188f3dfcb4c1b","tid":2286603,"uid":16659,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:39:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201115/404455386242879488158264.jpeg/tpV-3PYYVG-7buBLdixbDcdKNg5UW9iNzUMsNs1DLDY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201115%2F404455386242879488158264.jpeg%2FtpV-3PYYVG-7buBLdixbDcdKNg5UW9iNzUMsNs1DLDY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=2a542cf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201115/404455388923170816579320.jpeg/7PINC4Z_rPXlFAMKYO0GP4aYCXp0f-Bnm549pZuePaU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201115%2F404455388923170816579320.jpeg%2F7PINC4Z_rPXlFAMKYO0GP4aYCXp0f-Bnm549pZuePaU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=1451dd77&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92b078a984c962ace6542f78a484d16f4001533d","tid":2286603,"uid":229026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:39:45.000Z","msg":"會唔會太癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd3190f0d18d1f95a05981c0f306e0a6af3bc7c8","tid":2286603,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:40:37.000Z","msg":"好嫁唔嫁 嫁埋啲教徒<img src=\"/as